            <h3 style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; color: #222222;">(3) Thanh toán trực tuyến (bằng thẻ ATM, VISA, MASTER):</span></h3>
